  "description": "Okay, so at the end of my last babble, I said that I was going to migrate from MkDocs to Astro, after having only just recently moved to MkDocs, and in fact not even fully completed that migration.\nWell, after trying to get links-in-Obsidian to work nicely with links-in-Astro, I gave up, went looking for another solution, and found Quartz.\nBut, on my way there, I found Diátaxis, \u0026ldquo;a way of thinking about and doing documentation\u0026rdquo; - specifically, technical documentation.\n",
